{"image_id": "OXY_2018_page_16", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "5", "bbox": [607.9, 1574.0, 618.3, 1594.9]}, {"text": "MIDSTREAM AND MARKETING OPERATIONS", "bbox": [75.0, 69.9, 525.4, 90.7]}, {"text": "General", "bbox": [75.0, 94.0, 144.9, 112.7]}, {"text": "Occidental's midstream and marketing operations", "bbox": [112.5, 116.9, 582.3, 136.7]}, {"text": "primarily support and enhance its oil and gas and chemical", "bbox": [75.0, 140.7, 582.3, 160.5]}, {"text": "businesses and also provide similar services for third", "bbox": [75.0, 164.4, 582.3, 184.2]}, {"text": "parties.", "bbox": [75.0, 188.2, 145.5, 208.0]}, {"text": "In 2018, Occidental sold  several non-core assets,", "bbox": [112.5, 212.0, 582.3, 231.7]}, {"text": "including the Centurion common carrier oil pipeline and", "bbox": [75.0, 235.7, 582.3, 255.5]}, {"text": "storage system, Southeast New Mexico oil gathering", "bbox": [75.0, 259.5, 582.3, 279.3]}, {"text": "system and Ingleside Crude Terminal. Following the", "bbox": [75.0, 283.2, 582.3, 303.0]}, {"text": "transactions, Occidental retained its long-term flow", "bbox": [75.0, 307.0, 582.3, 326.8]}, {"text": "assurance, pipeline takeaway and export capacity through", "bbox": [75.0, 330.7, 582.3, 350.5]}, {"text": "its retained marketing business.", "bbox": [75.0, 354.5, 353.4, 374.3]}, {"text": "Also within the midstream and marketing segment is", "bbox": [689.3, 69.9, 1159.1, 89.7]}, {"text": "Oxy Low Carbon Ventures (OLCV). OLCV seeks to", "bbox": [651.8, 93.7, 1159.1, 113.5]}, {"text": "capitalize on Occidental’s EOR leadership by developing", "bbox": [651.8, 117.4, 1159.0, 137.2]}, {"text": "carbon capture, utilization and storage projects that source", "bbox": [651.8, 141.2, 1159.1, 161.0]}, {"text": "anthropogenic carbon dioxide and promote innovative", "bbox": [651.8, 165.0, 1159.0, 184.7]}, {"text": "technologies that drive cost efficiencies and economically", "bbox": [651.8, 188.7, 1159.1, 208.5]}, {"text": "grow Occidental’s